" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Atrial fibrillation increases mortality in men and women",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 406px; height: 260px; background-image: url(data:image/gif;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Among 5209 subjects in the Framingham Heart Study, the mortality after a 10-year follow-up was higher in both men and women, aged 55 to 74, who had atrial fibrillation (AF) compared to those without AF (p &lt;0.001) A similar relationship was seen in subjects between the ages of 75 and 94 (not shown).",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
